### üß© `function schemaS`

```ts
type FunctionSchema = {
  name: string; // Unique identifier
  description?: string; // Optional explanation of the function
  input: {
    [key: string]: {
      type: string;
      required: boolean;
      description?: string;
      default?: any;
      enum?: string[];
      pattern?: string;
    };
  };
  output: {
    type: string;
    description?: string;
    structure?: object;
  };
  triggers?: string[]; // e.g. voice, CLI, HTTP
  permissions?: string[]; // e.g. ['admin', 'agent', 'operator']
  tags?: string[]; // e.g. ['ritual', 'bounty', 'drop', 'voice']
};
```

