#### üß† `runCulturalScan`

Scans cultural sources (TikTok, Threads, Ko-fi, Discord) every `10min` or `6h`.

```ts
{
  name: "runCulturalScan",
  input: {
    mode: { type: "string", required: true, enum: ["10min", "6h"] },
    includeFeedback: { type: "boolean", required: false, default: true }
  },
  output: {
    type: "object",
    structure: {
      trendTriggers: "string[]",
      viralHeatIndex: "number",
      actions: "string[]"
    }
  },
  triggers: ["cron", "manual"],
  permissions: ["godmode", "agent"],
  tags: ["scanloop", "taskGPT", "climate"]
}
```

